* Iron Raptor heard people nearing the controle room door, looking over her 
shoulder and seeing just who they were.
Firedrill, Beachcomber and Cliffjumper.
Firedrill she knew but the other two were new to her.
There were so many Maximals it was hard to keep track of them all.
While waiting for a responce she spoke up.*

" You three, go and see that's going on outside. Two of you stay out there 
and one come back here to give me a detailed report on what's happening."

* This was no time to be nice, there were charges going off outside, a
transmission to be figured out...and so on so forth.*
